                %p Current health systems focus is on clinical care. However, it is necessary to view health as a holistic measure of an individual's entire living situation and life experience. These factors that strongly affect an individuals overall quality of health are the <span style="font-weight: bold">determinants of health</span>.
                %p Extending far beyond medical care, these factors can be used to improve health within the clinical, population, and public health spaces.

